data.description: Live the lake life! Lake Attitash fixer-upper loaded with potential. 2000 SFLA, currently three bedrooms, open concept with a guest suite, two mini-splits for heat & AC. Offering water views, one lot & steps away from Lake Attitash, a newer metal roof, carport, shed, and firepit area for roasting marshmallows on summer nights. Merrimac has a brand new, state-of-the-art Pentucket middle & high school. Reasonable utility costs with Merrimac Light. Offers will be reviewed on Monday, May 22 at noon. Sold in as-is condition. PARKING IS VERY LIMITED. PLEASE PARK IN THE TOWN BOAT LAUNCH PARKING AREA AND WALK OVER TO PINE BLUFF.
